## Limitations

The findings in this report are based on available literature and may not encompass all cultural contexts. The complexity of cultural influences on gender roles means that some nuances may not be fully captured. Additionally, the reliance on secondary sources may introduce biases inherent in the original research. Future studies could benefit from primary research and a broader range of cultural perspectives to provide a more comprehensive analysis.

